{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">练习连接家庭电路。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用电器并联在家庭电路中。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家庭电路、插座、灯座、灯泡、开关</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.观察家庭电路的电能表、总开关、保险丝，火线、零线等，将灯座的红色接线头连到开关的一个接线柱上，开关的另一端接在家庭电路的火线上（红线），</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">灯座的蓝色接线头连接家庭电路的零线（蓝线）；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.将灯泡接在灯座上，打开开关，观察灯泡是否发光；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.将三孔插座的红色接线头接在火线上（红线），蓝色接线柱接在零线上（蓝线），黄色接线柱接在地线上（黄线）；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.将用电器插在插座上观察是否工作。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">家用电器并联在家庭电路中。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三孔插座上的接地线和用电器的金属外壳相连，插座上相应的导线和室外的大地相连，万一用电器的外壳和电源火线之间的绝缘损坏，使外壳带电，电流会流入大地，不致对人造成伤害。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}